Goal
----
A calendar program which can:
  I) handle appointments and tasks specified in a plaintext file
    A) one-time and
    B) scheduled
      1) arbitrarily
      2) regularly by
        a) day of week
        b) day of month (like a meniversary)
        c) day of month (like First Fridays or Thanksgiving)
        d) day of year
        e) relative to any of these (like Thursday before First Friday, or
           Friday after last completion)
        f) goal: an automated liturgical calendar or school schedule
  II) display them
    A) in a GUI
    B) with curses
